## 1 ##
alpha = 2
L = 10
m = 501
n = 128
xspan = np.linspace(-L,L,n+1)[:-1]
tspan = np.linspace(0,2,m)

dt = tspan[1] - tspan[0]
dx = xspan[1] - xspan[0]

u_0 = 10*np.cos(2*np.pi*xspan/L) + 30*np.cos(8*np.pi*xspan/L)
lmbd_star = alpha*dt/(dx**2)

####
def g_14(z,lmbd):
    g = 1 + (lmbd/6)*(16*np.cos(z) - np.cos(2*z) - 15)
    return g

A1 = np.abs(g_14(1,lmbd_star))

onefour_star_g = lambda z: g_14(z,lmbd_star)
z_14_opt= sp.optimize.fminbound(lambda z: -onefour_star_g(z), -np.pi, np.pi)

A2 = np.abs(g_14(z_14_opt, lmbd_star))

#####
e1 = np.ones(n)
D4 = sp.sparse.spdiags([16*e1, -1*e1,-1*e1,16*e1,-30*e1,16*e1, -1*e1,-1*e1,16*e1],
                       [-n+1,-n+2,-2,-1,0,1,2,n-2,n-1], n,n, format ='csc')/12

A3 = D4.todense()

####
u_14 = np.zeros((len(xspan),len(tspan)))
u_14[:,0] = u_0

tic = time.time()
for i in range(len(tspan)-1):
    u_14[:,i+1] = u_14[:,i] + lmbd_star*D4@u_14[:,i]
time_14 = time.time() - tic
    
A5 = u_14[:,-1].reshape(-1,1)

## 2 ##
def g_cn(z,lmbd):
    g = (lmbd*np.cos(z) + (1-lmbd))/((1+lmbd) - lmbd*np.cos(z))
    return g

cn_star_g = lambda z: g_cn(z,lmbd_star)
z_cn_opt= sp.optimize.fminbound(lambda z: -cn_star_g(z), -np.pi, np.pi)

A6 = np.abs(g_cn(z_cn_opt, lmbd_star))

####
B = sp.sparse.spdiags([-lmbd_star/2*e1, (1+lmbd_star)*e1, -lmbd_star/2*e1],
                      [-1,0,1],n,n,format='csc')
B[-1,0] = -lmbd_star/2
B[0,-1] = -lmbd_star/2

C = sp.sparse.spdiags([lmbd_star/2*e1, (1-lmbd_star)*e1, lmbd_star/2*e1],
                      [-1,0,1],n,n,format='csc')
C[-1,0] = lmbd_star/2
C[0,-1] = lmbd_star/2

A7 = B.todense()
A8 = C.todense()

####
u_cn = np.zeros((len(xspan), len(tspan)))
u_cn[:,0] = u_0

lu_solver = sp.sparse.linalg.splu(B)

tic = time.time()
for i in range(len(tspan)-1):
    u_cn[:,i+1] = lu_solver.solve(C@u_cn[:,i])
time_cn = time.time() - tic

A9 = u_cn[:,-1].reshape(-1,1)

####
u_bc = np.zeros((len(xspan), len(tspan)))
u_bc[:,0] = u_0

tic = time.time()
for i in range(len(tspan)-1):
    u_bc[:,i+1], _ = sp.sparse.linalg.bicgstab(B, C@u_bc[:,i], x0 = u_bc[:,i])
time_bc = time.time() - tic

A10 = u_bc[:,-1].reshape(-1,1)

## Presentation 1(a) ##
drive = 'G'

exact_128 = np.genfromtxt(f'{drive}:/Other/UW/AMATH 481/hw4/exact_128.csv',delimiter = ',')
exact_256 = np.genfromtxt(f'{drive}:/Other/UW/AMATH 481/hw4/exact_256.csv',delimiter = ',')
exact_512 = np.genfromtxt(f'{drive}:/Other/UW/AMATH 481/hw4/exact_512.csv',delimiter = ',')
exact_1024 = np.genfromtxt(f'{drive}:/Other/UW/AMATH 481/hw4/exact_1024.csv',delimiter = ',')

def one_a_solver(n,lmbd_star,exact,fe_or_cn):        
    L = 10
    alpha = 2
    
    xspan = np.linspace(-L,L,n+1)[:-1]
    dx = xspan[1]-xspan[0]
    dt = lmbd_star*(dx**2)/alpha ## ensure CFL is same by getting dt
    tspan = np.arange(0,2+dt,dt)
    
    u_0 = 10*np.cos(2*np.pi*xspan/L) + 30*np.cos(8*np.pi*xspan/L)
    
    e1 = np.ones(n)
    
    if fe_or_cn == 0: ## FE-(1,4) Scheme
        D4_n = sp.sparse.spdiags([16*e1, -1*e1,-1*e1,16*e1,-30*e1,16*e1, -1*e1,-1*e1,16*e1],
                                [-n+1,-n+2,-2,-1,0,1,2,n-2,n-1], n,n, format ='csc')/12
    
        u_14_n = np.zeros((len(xspan),len(tspan)))
        u_14_n[:,0] = u_0
        
        for i in range(len(tspan)-1):
            u_14_n[:,i+1] = u_14_n[:,i] + lmbd_star*D4_n@u_14_n[:,i]
            
        error = np.linalg.norm(exact - u_14_n[:,-1])
    
    elif fe_or_cn == 1 or 2: ## Crank-Nicolson
        B_n = sp.sparse.spdiags([-lmbd_star/2*e1, (1+lmbd_star)*e1, -lmbd_star/2*e1],
                        [-1,0,1],n,n,format='csc')
        B_n[-1,0] = -lmbd_star/2
        B_n[0,-1] = -lmbd_star/2

        C_n = sp.sparse.spdiags([lmbd_star/2*e1, (1-lmbd_star)*e1, lmbd_star/2*e1],
                        [-1,0,1],n,n,format='csc')
        C_n[-1,0] = lmbd_star/2
        C_n[0,-1] = lmbd_star/2
        
        u_cn_n = np.zeros((len(xspan), len(tspan)))
        u_cn_n[:,0] = u_0
        if fe_or_cn == 1: ## LU decomp
            lu_solver_n = sp.sparse.linalg.splu(B_n)

            for i in range(len(tspan)-1):
                u_cn_n[:,i+1] = lu_solver_n.solve(C_n@u_cn_n[:,i])
        
        elif fe_or_cn == 2: ## BICGSTAB
            for i in range(len(tspan)-1):
                u_cn_n[:,i+1], _ = sp.sparse.linalg.bicgstab(B_n, C_n@u_cn_n[:,i], x0 = u_cn_n[:,i])
        
        error = np.linalg.norm(exact - u_cn_n[:,-1]) ## calculate error
        
    else:
        return print("Please choose either $\texttt{fe_or_cn = 0, 1, or 2}$")
    return error, dx

points = [128,256,512,1024]
lmbd_star = 0.32768

errors = np.zeros((4,3))
dxs = np.zeros(4)
slopes = np.zeros((3,2))

for j in range(3):
    for i, data in enumerate([exact_128,exact_256,exact_512,exact_1024]):
        errors[i,j], dxs[i] = one_a_solver(points[i], lmbd_star = lmbd_star, exact = data, fe_or_cn=j)
    slopes[j,:] = np.polyfit(np.log(dxs), np.log(errors[:,j]), deg = 1)

color = ['k', 'r', 'royalblue']
title = ['FE - (1,4)','Crank-Nicolson (LU)', 'Crank-Nicolson (BICGSTAB)']
dxspan = 10**np.linspace(-2,-0.5,5)

fig, ax = plt.subplots(nrows = 1, ncols = 2, figsize = (9,6), sharey = True)
for i in range(2):
    ax[i].loglog(dxs,errors[:,i], 'o', color =color[i], label = 'Discrete Calculation')
    ax[i].loglog(dxspan,np.exp(slopes[i,1])*dxspan**(slopes[i,0]), color = color[i], 
                 label = f'Error$= O(\Delta x^n$) [n~= {np.round(slopes[i][0], decimals = 1)}]')
    ax[i].set_xlim([0.01,0.3])
    ax[i].set_ylim([0.0005,0.1])
    ax[i].set_title(title[i], fontsize = 17)
    ax[i].legend()
#    ax[i].grid(which = 'both')

ax[0].set_ylabel('Error', fontsize = 15)
fig.supxlabel('Order of $\Delta x$', fontsize = 15)  
fig.subplots_adjust(top = 0.87)
fig.suptitle('Heat Equation Error as a Function of $\Delta x$ for MOL Schemes', fontsize = 20)
fig.savefig('hw4_1a_presen.png')
